  Write a java program which will implements sum(int arr[]) method and will return sum of second max and second smallest element of array.
       Example : {1,2,1,1,3,4,5,4,5,5};
       Output : 6  (beacause second max is = 4 && second smallest is = 2 and the addition is = 6)

