     Write a Java program that finds and prints the second largest element in an integer array. 
       Given an array of integers, the program should identify and output the second largest element present in the array. 
       For example, if the input array is {10, 1, 2, 10, 10, 9, 10, 10}, the output should be 9, as it is the second largest element in the array, after 10.

